wiki.summary: Date: 12 December 2008 Label: Salute Records, Sweden Narcotized is the first anti-islamic black metal split album by bands from the middle-east: Al-Namrood from Saudia Arabia, Dhul-Qarnayn from Bahrain, and Ayyur from Tunisia. Read more on Last.fm.
